1 (b) The department of agriculture and biosecurity shall
2 adopt rules in accordance with chapter 91 to implement this
3 section, including but not limited to establishing requirements
4 related to filament diameter, color, and the inclusion of visual
5 cues to prevent non-targeted entanglement [aftd]2_ prohibiting the
6 use of mist net material [that—io used] designed for bird
7 work[—]; and allowing the distribution and sale of fine mesh
8 nets, including monofilament netting of an appropriate mesh
9 size, for the sole purpose of protecting plants from the coconut
10 rhinoceros beetle (Oryctes rhinoceros)."
11 SECTION 3. Statutory material to be repealed is bracketed
12 and stricken. New statutory material is underscored.
13 SECTION 4. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
